      "message": "Ok, and I think I agree to that. We should probably figure out how to add links directly from the landing page to release notes, user guides etc in a structured way. What about dividing it into 'Release documentation' which should contain user guides, release notes etc. And then have a \"Developer documentation\" section with the rest? And more heading of course if needed.",
